267
00:29:12,729 --> 00:29:19,375
And we are really proud of what we've been able to do over the past three years with the community support.

268
00:29:19,955 --> 00:29:22,698
We are looking right now at a pretty critical transition year.

269
00:29:23,720 --> 00:29:28,945
We need to find a new long-term home for the location of the Mr. Community Market in Medford.

270
00:29:29,625 --> 00:29:33,889
We're working with city and commercial real estate partners at this time to find that.

271
00:29:34,529 --> 00:29:40,274
We are completely committed to keeping this program here in this city and for the Medford residents who need us.

272
00:29:41,435 --> 00:29:47,239
