273
00:29:47,399 --> 00:29:52,964
So we have been working hard to find private and public sources of ongoing operating support

274
00:29:53,445 --> 00:29:56,946
to maintain service levels, so your support's needed more than ever.

275
00:29:58,406 --> 00:30:08,429
We are asking for a pretty similar amount to prior years, and we anticipate that we'll continue to be able to sort of over-deliver on our promises with what we're able to do with it.

