00:39:36,630 --> 00:39:57,157
And I mean, I guess my thinking too is, you know, could we bring the different vendors together with the city to try to coordinate specific types of services and maybe, like, you know, I appreciate that the CDBG rules have their own specific thing and it's set by the federal government and it's 50 years old, but could we try to

